OL,3,CBus workers to be balloted on
OL,4,Cpotential strike action
OL,6,FBus drivers in Cornwall and Somerset
OL,7,Fare set to be balloted for strikes,
OL,8,Famid a growing number of disputes in
OL,9,Fthe sector.
OL,11,FMembers of the Rail, Maritime and
OL,12,FTransport union (RMT) at First South
OL,13,FWest will vote in the coming weeks on
OL,14,Fwhether to launch a campaign of
OL,15,Findustrial action.
OL,17,FThe dispute concerns pay, as the RMT
OL,18,Fcampaigns for the bus workers to move
OL,19,Fcloser to its "modest goal" of #15 an
OL,20,Fhour.
