OL,3,CBus workers to be balloted on
OL,4,Cpotential strike action
OL,6,FRMT general secretary Eddie Dempsey
OL,7,Fsaid: "Bus workers at First South West
OL,8,Fare being left behind while other
OL,9,Foperators across the region pay more."
OL,11,FA First Bus spokesperson said: "We
OL,12,Falways maintain open dialogue with
OL,13,Funions, and we're currently continuing
OL,14,Fpay negotiations.
OL,16,F"We don't want to pre-empt the outcome
OL,17,Fof those discussions, but we hope to
OL,18,Fcome to an agreement with the union
OL,19,Fand its members."
