OL,4,Cpotential strike action
OL,6,FMembers of Unite in several parts of
OL,7,Fthe country are involved in pay and
OL,8,Fconditions disputes, which have led to
OL,9,Fstrikes.
OL,11,FUnite members at Brighton Bus Company
OL,12,Fand the Metrobus Crawley company will
OL,13,Fstrike on October 6 and 15 after
OL,14,Frejecting a 3.5% pay offer.
